##Those returning to work | take their temperature four times a day and wear a mask except for meals

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Juret, thepaper.cn

Take your temperature four times a day. Wear a mask except when eating. This has become a daily routine since Leo (not his real name) returned to work.

He works in Equipment Management for a electronic component company in Chaozhou, Guangdong Province, and has been back to work for six days since the quarantine was lifted on December 12.

On Feb. 18, Leo told The Paper that the company had changed the landscape of the cafeteria. "In order to avoid face-to-face dining, the company has removed the stools on both sides of the dining hall so that people can only sit in one direction. " The faucets and hand sanitizers have also been replaced with inductive ones.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The company canteen can only be seated in the same direction. Source: All are provided to respondents

"every day I take the shuttle bus to work, and I can smell the disinfectant on the bus, " Leo said. Before boarding the bus, the driver will take the temperature of each passenger and take it again before entering the gate of the company. During the morning and afternoon shift, the Supervisor Registers the temperature of all employees again.

The lack of staff is Leo's deepest feeling since he returned to work. He used to be responsible for equipment management, but now he has to "treat one person as three people" , in addition to his job, he has to operate machinery and responsible for troubleshooting products. "I'm the only one of the five people we've recruited for the project at the same time, " he said at his normal job over the weekend.

"Now I'm afraid that the machine will break down, because if it does, it will involve all kinds of people looking for me. I can't get away from it, " Leo told thepaper.cn. The production volume of the company is not up to the required level, but it's not much different, and I'm still catching up.

They work mainly online, he says. When he had a problem, he often contacted his colleagues who had not come to the company by phone to help him solve it.

Leo said that because of the new pneumonia epidemic, the company's original notice of starting work on the seventh day of the first lunar month had been delayed. At present, the company has not yet announced its official starting time, "But as long as the quarantine time is up, you can come to work, depending on your personal circumstances. " If colleagues in Hubei really can not come, there is no hard and fast requirement.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
The Faucet's switched to a sensor

For those who rush back to Chaozhou to return to work, the company offers three-person suites for those who need isolation. Packed lunches are delivered daily, and instant noodles, bread and milk are prepared for employees to choose from during the quarantine period.

Leo after the end of the quarantine period, back to his original dormitory, the company distributed disinfectant supplies. Rice, grain and oil, etc. , by special people in the vicinity of the supermarket to buy good delivery to the door.
